					&lt;p&gt;This is how limoncello is served in the province of Salerno (where it mainly comes from):&lt;/p&gt;

					&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://i.stack.imgur.com/MyxuO.jpg" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;&lt;img src="https://i.stack.imgur.com/MyxuO.jpg" alt="Limoncello"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

